        |   ArtWorks ClipArt CD1                                               |
        |                                                                      |
        |   "As a result of the 1993 ArtWorks clipart contest we received over |
        |   700 entries. This disc contains the majority of those, along with  |
        |   many other ArtWorks examples, and some high quality 24 bit         |
        |   photographs."                                                      |
        |                                                                      |
        |   - Contains over 700 ArtWorks files                                 |
        |   - Over 100 high-quality 24-bit images in TIFF and Acorn            |
        |     Sprite format                                                    |
        |   - !Portfolio file viewer and search utility, a quick way to find   |
        |     a particular ArtWorks, Sprite or TIFF file                       |
        |   - ArtWorks presentation                                            |
        |   - FontView utility to preview the 220 ArtWorks fonts               |
        |   - Example Matt Black draw files                                    |
        |   - ColourCard demonstration of 16bpp screen modes (suitable only    |
        |     for machines with ColourCard graphics accelerator cards)         |
        |                                                                      |
        |   NOTE: There is a small bug in !FontView which prevents it from     |
        |   working in screen mode 20.                                         |
        |                                                                      |
        |   Look out for a full release of ArtWorks in the coming months.      |
